snippet.title: GTFO Version 1.0 Launch Gameplay Trailer (4K)
snippet.description:
GTFO Version 1.0 is now available on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/493520/GTFO/

GTFO is a hardcore co-op FPS horror with high-intensity combat, tension-filled stealth, and team-based puzzle-solving for up to 4 players. In GTFO, you need to work together in order not to die together.

Join the official GTFO Discord at: https://discord.gg/gtfo
Become an Ambassador at: http://www.gtfothegame.com
Follow the game on Twitter @ https://twitter.com/gtfothegame

About 10 Chambers:
Founded in 2015, 10 Chambers is a game studio based in Stockholm, Sweden. The studio was founded by Ulf Andersson, who founded Overkill Software and was the brain behind PAYDAY 1 & 2. GTFO is the debut title from the studio. More information about 10 Chambers is available at www.10chambers.com. For press and media inquiries, contact robin@10chambers.com.

#GTFOtheGame
